-- Barclays Has No Plan to Spin Off Investment Unit, Telegraph Says
-- B y   M a r i a   K o l e s n i k o v a
-- 2012-07-15T15:35:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-15/barclays-has-no-plan-to-spin-off-investment-unit-telegraph-says.html
Barclays Plc (BARC)  has no plan to spin off
its investment banking unit, the Sunday Telegraph reported.  The bank remains committed to its strategy and business
model, the newspaper said, citing a Barclays e-mail to staff
last week.  Simon Eaton, a spokesman for Barclays, declined to comment
when reached by phone today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Maria Kolesnikova in London at 
 mkolesnikova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
